<section id="hero" class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-transparent">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 bg-white/95 p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 leading-tight">
          Ship your pre-seed SaaS MVP&mdash;fast, secure, and handoff-ready.
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          I build Rails prototypes and production MVPs with the SaaS foundations teams actually need: payments, accounts and multitenancy, OAuth logins, notifications, transactional email, and two-factor auth&mdash;hardened into maintainable software your next hire can scale.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl font-medium">
          Vibe-coding without a hardened engineer is about as useful as a PowerPoint slide. I use AI-accelerated tooling to move fast&mdash;and professional engineering practices to make it real.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-5 text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          Nine years of coding experience, including three years building my own apps and five years
          at a legal fintech as a backend, data lake, full stack, and SQL engineer.
        </p>

        <ul class="mt-8 space-y-3">
          <% [
            "Private equity fund admin: LP portals, capital calls, distribution waterfalls",
            "Venture capital legal tech: fund formation, compliance tracking, investor reporting",
            "Insurtech platforms: policy management, claims workflows, regulatory filings",
            "Billing and accounting systems: subscriptions, invoicing, reconciliation, metering",
            "Vanilla Rails patterns&mdash;teams can scale it later",
            "Regulated-domain UX: KYC onboarding, document generation, audit trails",
            "Security defaults: MFA, roles, least-privilege mindset",
          ].each do |bullet| %>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="size-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><%= bullet %></span>
            </li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <%= link_to "Book an MVP call", "#contact", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
          <%= link_to "See what you get out-of-the-box", "#capabilities", class: "btn btn-secondary btn-outline" %>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500 max-w-2xl">
          No hard sell. You&rsquo;ll leave with a plan.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-gray-100 rounded-full px-3 py-1">
            <span class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">$175/hr</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500">&middot; Senior Rails expertise</span>
          </span>
        </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-0 lg:col-span-5 flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="relative w-64 h-64 sm:w-72 sm:h-72 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg ring-1 ring-black/5">
            <%= image_tag "trev_prof_pic.PNG",
                  alt: "Trevor Nelson",
                  class: "size-full max-h-full max-w-full object-cover object-[center_18%] sm:object-[center_16%]" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md px-4 py-2 border border-gray-100 max-w-[calc(100%-1rem)]">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">(120x engineer)</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">+ expert network on call</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
